thread.title: BRIEF-Anhui Golden Seed Winery sees FY 2017 net profit down 47 pct to 76 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Anhui Golden Seed Winery sees FY 2017 net profit down 47 pct to 76 pct

organizations.name: anhui golden seed winery co ltd

text:
Feb 1(Reuters) - Anhui Golden Seed Winery Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to decrease by 47 percent to 76 percent, or to decrease by 8 million yuan to 13 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 17.0 million yuan
* The reason for the forecast is declined main business income
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/4p8pNN Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
